name: The Paradigm of Living Together
description:
Inspired by the cruelty of people who have a higher and wider power by silencing small citizens to obey inhuman rules.

The moral message conveyed is that if you are elected to respect the concerns of the people, then show your best performance, as well as when you whine for a voice from the community, rather than acting otherwise arbitrarily on the basis of having a higher position. and has broad powers.
